data.description: This charming South Redford bungalow is ready for new owners. Welcome to 13592 Berwyn featuring 3 bed's, 1 full bath, dinning room, full basement, 2 car detached garage and is located on a large lot. Pride of ownership really shows, with so many updates this home will not disappoint! Roof, windows, gutters and siding in 07', HVAC 19', basement water proofed with transferable warrenty 20', A/C 21', poured front porch and back patio in 22'.  This home is priced to move so schedule your appointment today!
